snippet.title: Supreme Court Refuses to Stay Plea against Note Ban in Lower Courts

localized.description:
The Supreme Court refuses to stay pleas against note ban in lower courts. Modi government has demonetised currency notes of Rs 500 and 1000 and peoples are struggling to exchange and withdraw cash at ATMs and banks.
